<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV3">
<l>aintumaintu maintumāki yallavaṟṟu ḷāyumāy</l>
<l>aintumūṉṟu moṉṟumāki niṉṟavāti tēvaṉē</l>
<l>aintumaintu maintumāki yantaratta ṇaintuniṉ</l>
<l>ṟaintumaintu māyaniṉṉai yāvarkāṇa vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O primordial Lord who</l>
<l rend="indent">—being [the master of] the five [elements], the five [organs of sensation],</l>
<l rend="indent">and the five [organs of action] that exist in those that do not exist—</l>
<l>have become the five [subtle elements] and the three [producers of creation]</l>
<l rend="indent">and the one [manas]!</l>
<l>Who is capable of perceiving You, who—being the five [immaterial forces],</l>
<l rend="indent">the five [organs of sensation], and the five [organs of action],</l>
<l>staying put in the sky—are the five [senses of enjoyment] and five [classes]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
